#: ../../../index.rst:-1
msgid "Vyper logo"
msgstr "Vyper 標誌"

#: ../../../index.rst:12
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概覽"

#: ../../../index.rst:14
msgid ""
"Vyper is a Pythonic smart contract language that compiles to `Ethereum "
"Virtual Machine (EVM) <https://ethereum.org/learn/#ethereum-basics>`_ "
"bytecode. It prioritises **security**, **auditability**, and **simplicity**."
msgstr ""
"Vyper 是一種 Python 式的智慧合約語言，它可以編譯成\\ `以太坊虛擬機（EVM） "
"<https://ethereum.org/learn/#ethereum-basics>`_\\ 位元組碼。它優先考慮安全"
"性、可稽核性和簡潔性 。"

#: ../../../index.rst:20
msgid "Principles"
msgstr "原則"

#: ../../../index.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Security**: Building secure smart contracts should be natural, not an "
"uphill battle."
msgstr ""
"**安全性**：建置安全的智慧合約應該是自然而然的事情，而不是一場艱苦的戰鬥。"

#: ../../../index.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Simplicity**: Both the language and compiler should be easy to understand."
msgstr "**簡潔性**：語言和編譯器都應該易於理解。"

#: ../../../index.rst:24
msgid ""
"**Auditability**: Code should be maximally human-readable. Simplicity for "
"the reader matters more than convenience for the writer."
msgstr ""
"**可稽核性**：程式碼應盡可能易於閱讀。對讀者而言，簡潔性比對編寫者而言的便利"
"性更為重要。"

#: ../../../index.rst:27
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "主要功能"

#: ../../../index.rst:29
msgid "**Safety by default**"
msgstr "**預設安全性**"

#: ../../../index.rst:31
msgid "Bounds and overflow checking on array accesses and arithmetic"
msgstr "陣列存取和算術運算的邊界與溢位檢查"

#: ../../../index.rst:32
msgid ""
"Reentrancy protection via the ``@nonreentrant`` decorator (see :ref:`control-"
"structures`)"
msgstr ""
"透過 ``@nonreentrant`` 裝飾器提供重入保護（請參閱 :ref:`control-structures`）"

#: ../../../index.rst:33
msgid "Strong typing with explicit :ref:`type conversions <type_conversions>`"
msgstr "強型別與明確的 :ref:`型別轉換 <type_conversions>`"

#: ../../../index.rst:35
msgid "**Predictable execution**"
msgstr "**可預測的執行**"

#: ../../../index.rst:37
msgid ""
"Decidable gas consumption: every function call has a calculable upper bound"
msgstr "可決定的 gas 消耗：每個函數呼叫都有可計算的上限"

#: ../../../index.rst:38
msgid "Bounded loops only (compile-time maximum iterations)"
msgstr "僅允許有界迴圈（編譯時期最大迭代次數）"

#: ../../../index.rst:39
msgid "No recursion: execution flow is structurally decreasing"
msgstr "無遞迴：執行流程在結構上是遞減的"

#: ../../../index.rst:41
msgid "**Clean code reuse**"
msgstr "**清晰的程式碼重用**"

#: ../../../index.rst:43
msgid ":ref:`Module imports <modules>` instead of class inheritance"
msgstr ":ref:`模組匯入 <modules>` 而非類別繼承"

#: ../../../index.rst:44
msgid ""
"Explicit ``extcall`` and ``staticcall`` keywords for external contract "
"interactions"
msgstr "明確的 ``extcall`` 和 ``staticcall`` 關鍵字用於外部合約互動"

#: ../../../index.rst:45
msgid ""
"Support for :ref:`pure functions <function-mutability>` that cannot modify "
"state"
msgstr "支援無法修改狀態的 :ref:`純函數 <function-mutability>`"

#: ../../../index.rst:48
msgid "Compiler-Enforced Security"
msgstr "編譯器強制執行的安全機制"

#: ../../../index.rst:50
msgid ""
"Vyper eliminates entire vulnerability classes by excluding features that "
"enable dangerous patterns:"
msgstr "Vyper 透過排除導致危險模式的功能來消除整個漏洞類別："

#: ../../../index.rst:56
msgid "Excluded Feature"
msgstr "排除的功能"

#: ../../../index.rst:57
msgid "Why It Matters"
msgstr "為何重要"

#: ../../../index.rst:58
msgid "Inline assembly"
msgstr "內聯組合語言"

#: ../../../index.rst:59
msgid ""
"Preserves type safety, overflow protection, and searchability of variable "
"usage"
msgstr "保留型別安全、溢位保護和變數使用的可搜尋性"

#: ../../../index.rst:60
msgid "Class inheritance"
msgstr "類別繼承"

#: ../../../index.rst:61
msgid "Removes ambiguity about which code executes and simplifies auditing"
msgstr "消除哪些程式碼會被執行的歧義，並簡化稽核"

#: ../../../index.rst:62
msgid "Modifiers"
msgstr "修改器"

#: ../../../index.rst:63
msgid "All checks are inline and visible, no hidden pre/post conditions"
msgstr "所有檢查都是內聯且可見的，沒有隱藏的前置/後置條件"

#: ../../../index.rst:64
msgid "Function overloading"
msgstr "函式覆載"

#: ../../../index.rst:65
msgid "Function calls are unambiguous; ``foo(x)`` always means the same thing"
msgstr "函數呼叫是明確的；``foo(x)`` 始終表示相同的意思"

#: ../../../index.rst:66
msgid "Operator overloading"
msgstr "運算子覆載"

#: ../../../index.rst:67
msgid "Arithmetic operators do exactly what they appear to do"
msgstr "算術運算子完全按照其表面意義執行"

#: ../../../index.rst:68
msgid "Infinite loops"
msgstr "無限迴圈"

#: ../../../index.rst:69
msgid "Gas costs are always bounded and predictable"
msgstr "燃料成本始終是有上限且可預測的"

#: ../../../index.rst:70
msgid "Recursive calls"
msgstr "遞迴呼叫"

#: ../../../index.rst:71
msgid "Call graphs are simple and gas limits are enforceable"
msgstr "呼叫圖簡單，且 gas 限制可強制執行"

#: ../../../index.rst:73
msgid ""
"These constraints mean developers cannot accidentally introduce dangerous "
"patterns, even under time pressure or with limited blockchain experience."
msgstr ""
"這些限制意味著開發者無法意外引入危險模式，即使在時間壓力或區塊鏈經驗有限的情"
"況下也是如此。"

#: ../../../index.rst:76
msgid "Deep Verification"
msgstr "深度驗證"

#: ../../../index.rst:78
msgid ""
"Vyper’s design makes **deep verification** practical on a production smart-"
"contract language."
msgstr "Vyper 的設計使\\ **深度驗證**\\ 在生產級智慧合約語言上變得可行。"

#: ../../../index.rst:80
msgid ""
"See :doc:`deep-verification` for the full discussion of verification depth, "
"verification gap, and the current state of Vyper’s formal semantics and "
"compiler verification work."
msgstr ""
"請參閱 :doc:`deep-verification` 以了解驗證深度、驗證差距以及 Vyper 的形式化語"
"意和編譯器驗證工作的目前狀態的完整討論。"

#: ../../../index.rst:83
msgid "Decimal Fixed Point"
msgstr "十進位定點數"

#: ../../../index.rst:85
msgid ""
"Vyper uses decimal (not binary) fixed point numbers. This ensures that "
"literals like ``0.1`` have exact representations, avoiding the subtle "
"precision errors common in binary floating-point arithmetic."
msgstr ""
"Vyper 使用十進位（非二進位）定點數。這確保像 ``0.1`` 這樣的字面值具有精確的表"
"示，避免了二進位浮點算術中常見的細微波動精度誤差。"
